Package shared.communication

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DownloadBatchResult
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Return a batch and a list of fields associate with the project id
    GetFieldsResult
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Return project id, field id and field title
    GetProjectsResult
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Return a list of ProjectModel from Project table
    GetSampleImage_Params
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Set and get username and pwd and project id
    GetSampleImageResult
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Return a URL of the sample image for the specific project
    GetSearch_Params
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Set and get username, pwd, field_id and search
    GetSearchResult
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Return a list of BatchModel and RecordModel for successful search
    SubmitBatch_Params
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Set and get username, pwd, batch_id and field value
    SubmitBatchResult
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Return boolean for result of the operation
    ValidateUser_Params
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Set and get username and pwd
    ValidateUserResult
    Communicator class that communicate with the client Return user parameters from UserModel table
